Considerations for Incremental Refreshes to Event Monitoring Analytics App Datasets

File uploads for some datasets end with the - Overwrite under the Origin column in Data Manager. This name change happens when event log file events have schema changes across release boundaries, such as when a new field is added.

The - Overwrite suffix can also appear when you enable time zone support. If you use time zone support, schedule your dataflow to run daily.

For large datasets, the daily dataflow runtime for incremental dataset updates takes longer than full dataset updates.

Incremental dataset refreshes delete raw data from datasets.
Dataset API names are generated dynamically during app creation. We recommend that you donâ€™t couple integrations with the Event Monitoring Analytics app with dataset API names.
